{"tid":1116954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解單車館火警會開天窗?","createTime":"2019-04-20T10:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T11:30:27.000Z","uid":161069,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"30e6080fea689d5df27aa0eccaf09c026d2c56de","tid":1116954,"uid":161069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T10:50:46.000Z","msg":"今日單車館話因為火警鐘誤鳴所以開天窗<br />\n但點解會設計到火警既時候開天窗？<br />\n要疏散人群又用唔著天窗<br />\n直升機掉水彈又唔及消防拉水喉<br />\n唔通係要黎做對流等個火燒勁d可以重新起過增加GDP<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12ae7086d032cf110107178a0d61cfeec61a5b4","tid":1116954,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T10:58:59.000Z","msg":"唔開窗咪焗死晒入面啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc0f965edd387e7bf9f6b847df0beb99984cde2","tid":1116954,"uid":93361,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T11:00:05.000Z","msg":"排煙"},{"pid":"3ec30842a6b0ed0d43a6618863199e0d9153228b","tid":1116954,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T11:01:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">等雨水淋熄啲火<br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢夢見其實唔係誤嗚，係淋熄左，啲人揾唔到火就話係誤嗚</span>"},{"pid":"cd92c2271e657933f8f7d2fd46a3332b15493e76","tid":1116954,"uid":161069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d12ae7086d032cf110107178a0d61cfeec61a5b4","tid":1116954,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T10:58:59.000Z","msg":"唔開窗咪焗死晒入面啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T11:29:58.000Z","msg":"佢有地下既出口可以走，點解要留係單車館入面"},{"pid":"5f764c57c302d64387179fb8dfcde2ba8a62e836","tid":1116954,"uid":161069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cc0f965edd387e7bf9f6b847df0beb99984cde2","tid":1116954,"uid":93361,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T11:00:05.000Z","msg":"排煙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T11:30: